This Resource describes functions for the control and monitoring of
The inverter status. The status can only be reset out of bounds.
The rated power in kW, defined at manufacturing time.
Minimum voltage for MPPT (Maximum power point tracking) control
Maximum voltage for MPPT (Maximum power point tracking) control
An RFC3339 formatted time indicating when the data was observed
